== 發射失敗 ==
=== Orbview-4發射失敗===
Orbview-4屬於[[地球之眼|地球之眼]]的衛星之一。在2001年9月21日發射，金牛座加大版火箭在剛開始發射成功，但最後[[衛星|衛星]]並沒到到達預定軌道。

=== 軌道碳偵測衛星發射失敗 ===
2009年2月35日發射，金牛座加大版火箭酬載著價值2.7億美元的'''[[軌道碳偵測|軌道碳偵測]]'''太空船<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/science/nature/7907570.stm |title=Failure hits Nasa's 'CO2 hunter' |accessdate=2011-08-15 |archive-date=2017-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107032848/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/science/nature/7907570.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在09:55(格林威治標準時間)成功的從范登堡空軍基地發射，但下一節無法分離，導致衛星無法到達到預定軌道<ref name="newscientist_oco">{{cite web|url=http://www.newscientist.com/article/dn16650-satellite-to-pinpoint-sources-and-sinks-of-co2.html|title=Satellite to pinpoint sources and sinks of CO2|accessdate=2011-08-15|archive-date=2010-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101127073710/http://www.newscientist.com/article/dn16650-satellite-to-pinpoint-sources-and-sinks-of-co2.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。軌道碳偵測花費在金牛座運載火箭及其周邊服務約5400萬美元<ref name="nasa_budget_estimates">{{Cite web |url=http://www.nasa.gov/pdf/210019main_NASA_FY09_Budget_Estimates.pdf |title=NASA FY2009 Budget Estimates |accessdate=2011-08-15 |archive-date=2014-03-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140311092444/http://www.nasa.gov/pdf/210019main_NASA_FY09_Budget_Estimates.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 輝煌號衛星發射失敗 ===
该卫星原定于2011年2月23日在[[范登堡空军基地|范登堡空军基地]]通过金牛座XL火箭火箭发射升空<ref>{{cite web | title =Launch Schedule | publisher =NASA | url =http://www.nasa.gov/missions/highlights/schedule.html | date =December 8, 2010 | accessdate =2010-12-17 | archive-date =2019-01-29 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20190129135246/https://www.nasa.gov/missions/highlights/schedule.html | dead-url =no }}</ref>，后因故推迟了数日<ref>{{cite web  | title =NASA Assessing New Launch Dates For The Glory Mission  | publisher =NASA  | url =http://www.nasa.gov/home/hqnews/2011/feb/HQ_M11-056_Glory_Delay.html  | date =2011-02-24  | accessdate =2011-03-03  | archive-date =2011-02-27  | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20110227015856/http://www.nasa.gov/home/hqnews/2011/feb/HQ_M11-056_Glory_Delay.html  | dead-url =no  }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title =NASA's Glory Satellite Scheduled for Launch on March 4 | publisher =NASA | url =http://www.nasa.gov/home/hqnews/2011/mar/HQ_M11-041_Glory_Launch_Day.html | date =2011-03-04 | accessdate =2011-03-04 | archive-date =2011-03-04 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20110304001055/http://www.nasa.gov/home/hqnews/2011/mar/HQ_M11-041_Glory_Launch_Day.html | dead-url =no }}</ref>。

2011年3月4日，火箭升空六分钟后，[[整流罩|整流罩]]没有正确的与火箭分离，卫星未能进入预定轨道<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-12551861|title=Nasa Glory mission ends in failure|publisher=BBC News|4=|date=2011-03-04|accessdate=2011-03-04|archive-date=2011-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110305052725/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-12551861|dead-url=no}}</ref>，整体坠入[[太平洋|太平洋]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.sina.com.cn/w/2011-03-04/234922054975.shtml|title=美国地球观测卫星发射失败坠入太平洋|publisher=新浪网|date=2011-03-04|accessdate=2011-03-05|archive-date=2011-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110308043614/http://news.sina.com.cn/w/2011-03-04/234922054975.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="#1"/>。这次失败与两年前美国軌道碳偵測卫星坠落事故十分相似<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tech.sina.com.cn/d/2009-02-24/23582854835.shtml|title=美国嗅碳卫星发射失败坠入南极附近海域|publisher=新浪科技|date=2009-02-24|accessdate=2011-03-04|archive-date=2009-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090227101408/http://tech.sina.com.cn/d/2009-02-24/23582854835.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。輝煌號衛星造價約4.24億美元，屬於氣候變遷偵測衛星。

== 陸基中途防禦 ==
{{main |陸基中途防禦}}
與金牛座運載火箭相同的運載火箭被[[美國飛彈防禦局|美國飛彈防禦局]]作為'''陸基中途防禦系統'''之一<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.globalsecurity.org/space/systems/gbi-obv.htm |title=GBI Orbital Boost Vehicle |publisher=globalsecurity.org |accessdate=2011-08-15 |archive-date=2012-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120306040523/http://www.globalsecurity.org/space/systems/gbi-obv.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
==金牛座2號運載火箭==
{{main |金牛座2號運載火箭}}
軌道科學公司正在籌劃金牛座2號運載火箭，預計第一節將使用[[液態燃料發動機|液態燃料發動機]]，與金牛座1號運載火箭不同，首次發射定在2011年第三季<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.orbital.com/TaurusII/ |title=Orbital Sciences Corporation |accessdate=2011-08-15 |archive-date=2009-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091030074601/http://www.orbital.com/TaurusII/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。最終名稱為[[安塔瑞斯運載火箭|安塔瑞斯運載火箭]]，並於2013年4月21日首次飛行測試成功<ref name="軌道科學公司">{{Cite web|url=http://www.orbital.com/Antares-Cygnus/ |title=Cargo Resupply Services |author= |date= |publisher=[[軌道科學公司|軌道科學公司]] |language=en |accessdate=2013年4月23日 |quote= |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130417064631/http://www.orbital.com/antares-cygnus/ |archivedate=2013年4月17日 }}</ref>。

